   - The `"value"_c` syntax uses the user-defined literal to reference the column

3. **`sqlgen::create_as<Target>(filtered_query)`**:
   - Creates a CREATE TABLE AS SELECT statement
   - The Target table structure will be inferred from the selected columns
   - The query will create a new table with the same structure as the selected columns

